### Get Inspirational Quote
### Returns the AI-generated inspirational quote based on user's last 20 journal entries
### Includes 4 thematic tags extracted from journal themes
### Regenerates when: user creates new entry, once per day, or if no quote exists

GET {{base_url}}/api/inspiration
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Expected Response (200 OK):
# {
#   "id": "uuid",
#   "quote": "Your personalized inspirational quote here...",
#   "tags": ["growth", "reflection", "gratitude", "mindfulness"],
#   "generatedAt": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z",
#   "updatedAt": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
# }

### Expected Response (404 Not Found - No quote yet):
# {
#   "message": "No inspirational quote generated yet. One will be created shortly based on your journal entries."
# }
